The CdSe NPLs were synthesised according to a previously reported method32. The synthesised NPLs had lateral dimensions of 50–100 nm × 100–200 nm according to transmission electron microscopy (TEM) (Fig. S1). The uniform thickness of 1.4 nm was confirmed by the sharp excitonic peak at 453 nm in the ultraviolet–visible (UV–Vis) extinction spectrum, which is in good agreement with the reported value of 451 nm (Fig. S2). X-ray diffraction (XRD) analysis confirmed their crystal structure to be wurtzite, with ±(112¯0)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
